               (instead of isBeginningDateOf)."""@en ],
        [ dc:date "2023-09-22" ;
            rdf:value "Added in RiC-O 1.0."@en ],
        [ dc:date "2023-10-12" ;
            rdf:value "Added the French label"@en ],
        [ dc:date "2025-02-19" ;
            rdf:value "Changed definition (added \\"or will be\\")."@en ] .

:isPublisherOf a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:label "is publisher of"@en,
        "es editor(a) de"@es,
        "est l’éditeur de"@fr ;
    rdfs:comment """Connects an Agent to a Record Resource that it
